  "title": "Safety Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job Requirements: </p><ul><li>Registered with Ministry of Manpower (MOM) and possess the necessary requirements of a Workplace Safety & Health Officer (WSHO) as required by MOM, or similar Qualifications and Experience acceptable to HDB.</li></ul><p>Job Description: </p><ul><li>To assist the Project Manager in planning, formulating, supervising and implementing safety programs/ safety initiatives.</li></ul><ul><li>To conduct regular safety inspections and safety audits to identify hazards orareas where safety measures can be improved.</li></ul><ul><li>To supervise and ensure that all WSHOs employed by the Contractor are performing their roles satisfactorily and review all safety proposals and submit monthly reports to HDB. </li></ul><ul><li>To ensure proper documentation of compliance with safety regulations and internal safety standards</li></ul><ul><li>To collaborate with the Project Manager to prepare reports for management regarding incidents, safety trends and recommendations for improvements.</li></ul><p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:HR@sg.tylin.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">HR@sg.tylin.com</a><strong></strong></p><p>Submit resume with photo including current and expected salary and contact no. latest by 28 February 2026.</p>",
