    "description": "<p><strong>T.Y. Lin International PTE LTD</strong> is multi award winning Singapore based multi-disciplinary engineering services firm. An affiliate office of T.Y. Lin International based in San Francisco, USA and a member of the internationally acclaimed Dar Al-Handasah Group. T.Y. Lin International has more than 2,500 professionals in 50 offices throughout the Americas and Asia.</p>\n<p>The Singapore Office has been serving the engineering needs of Singapore and the Region for over forty years and we pride ourselves in our approach and our ability to deliver a consistently high quality of service to our clients.Our core business includes civil, structural, mechanical, electrical, geotechnical and railway engineering services from concept planning through to implementation, construction, operation and maintenance.</p>\n<p>T.Y. Lin International has been instrumental in the delivery of a wide range of projects across Singapore and the Region including Mass Rapid Transit (MRT) stations and tunnels, highway projects and several bridges including Keppel Bay Bridge and Hledan Flyover, Myanmar, hotel/recreational complex developments such as Marina Bay Sands Integrated Resort, multiple complex and high rise building developments including The Interlace Condominium and many more.</p>",
